{"lemma":"أَسَنَّيْ","slug":"أَسَنَّيْ","root":"س.ن.ن","root_slug":"س-ن-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ن-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَسَنّ","root":"أسن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n785","n786","n20840","n20865"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grow teeth, to cut one’s teeth, to teethe","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to furnish with a toothlike projection (for example, a pointy end, a blade, and so on)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to advance in years, to grow old, to age","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"with more or stronger teeth; with the most or strongest teeth"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"older; oldest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of سِنّ (sinn)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Partially from the root س ن ن (s n n). In senses relating to aging, directly derived from سَنَة (sana, “a year”).\n\nElative from the root س ن ن (s n n); compare سِنّ (sinn, “tooth, age”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n785","headword_ar":"اَسَنَ","root":"Asn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usuwnN","text_ar":"اُسُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asonN","text_ar":"اَسْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asina","text_ar":"اَسِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asanN","text_ar":"اَسَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb;) said of water,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajana","text_ar":"اَجَنَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajina","text_ar":"اَجِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became altered for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Mgh, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in odour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in taste and colour, from some such cause as long standing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajana","text_ar":"اَجَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but was drinkable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as not to be drunk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) thus differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajana","text_ar":"اَجَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajina","text_ar":"اَجِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSila","text_ar":"اَصِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n786","headword_ar":"اَسِنٌ","root":"Asn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20840","headword_ar":"اسنّ","root":"sn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, L, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isonaAnN","text_ar":"اـِسْنَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, L, Msb,) said of a man, (S, M, L, Msb, K,) and of other than man, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kabira","text_ar":"كَبِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became advanced in age,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fullgrown"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, L, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kabirato sin~uhu","text_ar":"كَبِرَتْ سِنُّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means the same]; (M, L, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astsn~","text_ar":"استسنّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) but Az says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_isonaAnu","text_ar":"الاـِسْنَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the case of an animal of the ox-kind and of the sheep or goat, is not the same as in that of a man: for in such animals it means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the attaining to the age of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the coming forth of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"permanent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~ap","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"central incisor"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) or in such animals it means at least ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the attaining to the age of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the shedding of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tooth called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vny~p","text_ar":"ثنيّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is generally said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the third year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and at the utmost in such animals, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the attaining to the age of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~uluwg","text_ar":"الصُّلُوغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~uluwg","text_ar":"السُّلُوغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sixth year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and at the utmost in camels, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the attaining to the age of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albuzuwl","text_ar":"البُزُول"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is generally"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the ninth year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh, L.) [It is also expl. in the K as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His tooth grew forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but the right explanation is one given in the Mgh and L; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his tooth whereby he became"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masin~","text_ar":"مَسِنّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grew forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamo yusonano","text_ar":"لَمْ يُسْنَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a trad. of Ibn-'Omar, as some relate it, is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamo yusonino","text_ar":"لَمْ يُسْنِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albadanapu","text_ar":"البَدَنَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sun~ati","text_ar":"سُنَّتِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", a phrase mentioned by Kt, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The teeth of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bdnp","text_ar":"بدنة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grew forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a mistake [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asan~at","text_ar":"اَسَنَّت"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b2-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Asn~ sadiysu Aln~aAqapi","text_ar":"اسنّ سَدِيسُ النَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tooth called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sdys","text_ar":"سديس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the she-camel grew forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the eighth year."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.)       -A2-  Also, said of God,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"a tooth"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to grow forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"san~ahaA","text_ar":"سَنَّهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [referring to the teeth of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badanap","text_ar":"بَدَنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",] a phrase mentioned by Kt, is a mistake [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asan~ahaA","text_ar":"اَسَنَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b2-  See also 1, in the former half of the paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","M","L","Msb","K","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n20865","headword_ar":"اـَسَنُّ","root":"sn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"advanced in age:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K:) a correct Arabic word. (M, L.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA A^asan~u mino h`*aA","text_ar":"هٰذَا اَسَنُّ مِنْ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is more advanced in age than this:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K: *) and Th says, speaking of Moosà Ibn-'Eesà-Leythee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorakotuhu A^asan~a","text_ar":"اَدْرَكْتُهُ اَسَنَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholi Albaladi","text_ar":"اَهْلِ البَلَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I lived in his time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"he"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being the most advanced in age of the people of the town,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, L.)"}],"source_refs":["M","L","K"]}]}}